{"tid":2009604,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"愛國歌手劉樂妍最新單曲「CHINA」電爆垃圾台毒覺青仔","createTime":"2020-05-10T00:51:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-10T01:47:11.000Z","uid":52658,"like":2,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"1ca054df7ec5cc658dbcc024707cb9efa2df8bf4","tid":2009604,"uid":52658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T00:51:47.000Z","msg":"被封為「女版黃安」的劉樂妍過去爭議不斷，日前甚至強調「中國是現在全世界最安全的地方！」讓不少台灣網民看傻了眼。近日她從未曝光的單曲〈CHINA〉，突然被放上YouTube播出，再度引來網路惡評。MV曝光後，劉樂妍不滿在微博發文，強調這支MV花了上百萬拍攝卻拍壞了，更坦言「我要扔掉了，這是垃圾。」<br />\n<br />\n該單曲曝光後，劉樂妍近日在微博分享多則媒體相關報導，寫下：「我翻不了牆，不知道台灣媒體哪一家在報導，這個MV，花了100萬，拍壞了，整支我都不要了，所以我從來沒有宣傳過，我要扔掉了，這是垃圾。」質疑是有心人士將MV外流，更痛罵「你們偷了一個我根本不要宣傳的MV，High成這樣真的好像智障哦，天哪」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/oiV289MYNeY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FoiV289MYNeY&d=EEWyN02WlTtsLATURr%2FfpXhUmc0vP2awQoWdJLgJf%2FY%3D&h=b29368bd\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/oiV289MYNeY</a>"},{"pid":"81a71663ad032edbd82378056460a4c909f635dc","tid":2009604,"uid":63311,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T00:56:33.000Z","msg":"得到了愛支病"},{"pid":"9535d17d15fbd850dae6f659eea815480eed4113","tid":2009604,"uid":238370,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T01:02:05.000Z","msg":"佢話CHINA是垃圾？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b65c8d04eb6e4faf023028481dc42d5c78fa386c","tid":2009604,"uid":310446,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T01:06:16.000Z","msg":"呢啲咪叫輸打贏要囉<br />\n<br />\n哎呀Sor 條友冇贏過<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06d64bd58dccdd4e692ffc264d5953ff0e2f8d63","tid":2009604,"uid":52658,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"81a71663ad032edbd82378056460a4c909f635dc","tid":2009604,"uid":63311,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime